You got it all over your head.

00:35:32.320 --> 00:35:35.119
*With bamboo staff and straw sandals, lighter than a horse...*

00:35:35.599 --> 00:35:38.840
*In the scent of rice blossoms, we speak of a bountiful year.*

00:35:40.079 --> 00:35:43.760
*This period of time will be deeply etched in my heart.*

00:35:44.639 --> 00:35:45.719
*Here,*

00:35:46.159 --> 00:35:48.639
*I touched the most ordinary,*

00:35:48.920 --> 00:35:50.800
Yet most vivid, the fireworks of human life.

00:35:51.239 --> 00:35:53.320
*I met the most genuine,*

00:35:53.559 --> 00:35:55.360
*And most sincere friendships in the world.*

00:36:11.559 --> 00:36:15.079
*I've seen the cowardly who still choose courage,*

00:36:15.840 --> 00:36:18.840
*Answering the distant call with their footsteps.*

00:36:19.679 --> 00:36:21.079
*He chooses bravery,*

00:36:21.559 --> 00:36:22.880
*Not because fear is gone,*

00:36:23.800 --> 00:36:25.840
*But by carrying that clear,*

00:36:26.039 --> 00:36:27.599
*Trembling fear,*

00:36:28.119 --> 00:36:29.519
*Step by step,*

00:36:29.679 --> 00:36:30.960
*Walking towards a self,*

00:36:30.960 --> 00:36:32.559
*And a distant place never before reached.*

00:37:16.920 --> 00:37:18.400
*I've seen those bearing heavy burdens,*

00:37:18.400 --> 00:37:20.000
*Yet walking with calm composure,*

00:37:20.679 --> 00:37:24.119
*Gently reconciling with their ordinary selves in their stubbornness.*

00:37:24.760 --> 00:37:26.960
*He too once resented the ordinariness of fate,*

00:37:27.039 --> 00:37:29.679
*Wanting to live as someone extraordinary in others' eyes.*

00:37:30.480 --> 00:37:31.840
*Until one dusk,*

00:37:31.840 --> 00:37:33.199
*He finally understood,*

00:37:33.639 --> 00:37:34.960
*That true reconciliation*

00:37:34.960 --> 00:37:36.199
*Is not surrender,*

00:37:36.360 --> 00:37:38.519
*But seeing clearly one's own limits,*

00:37:38.679 --> 00:37:39.960
*And then gently*

00:37:39.960 --> 00:37:42.679
*Embracing that imperfect self.*

00:37:44.679 --> 00:37:46.880
*I've seen those with eternally blazing eyes,*

00:37:46.880 --> 00:37:48.280
*Full of energy,*

00:37:48.880 --> 00:37:51.119
*Becoming a shore others can lean on.*

00:37:51.800 --> 00:37:53.320
*Their palms*

00:37:53.320 --> 00:37:54.760
*May not always be warm,*

00:37:55.440 --> 00:37:57.039
*Yet always, at the crucial moment,*

00:37:57.039 --> 00:37:58.880
*Offer the most solid strength.*

00:38:12.199 --> 00:38:13.599
From them

00:38:13.679 --> 00:38:16.199
I glimpsed life's truest, grandest expanse

00:38:17.000 --> 00:38:18.960
The greatest endeavor in this world

00:38:18.960 --> 00:38:20.719
is none other than living well

00:38:21.159 --> 00:38:22.400
Living bravely

00:38:22.639 --> 00:38:23.840
Living diligently

00:38:24.840 --> 00:38:27.559
Eyes fixed straight ahead toward life's end

00:38:27.559 --> 00:38:28.960
and rushing toward it with abandon

00:38:29.960 --> 00:38:30.840
Thus

00:38:30.840 --> 00:38:33.039
I feel a happiness like never before

00:38:33.719 --> 00:38:35.079
This happiness

00:38:35.079 --> 00:38:37.960
comes not just from the fullness of each second lived

00:38:38.559 --> 00:38:40.320
but more so because within my life

00:38:40.400 --> 00:38:43.840
now resides a lasting hope

00:38:44.320 --> 00:38:46.480
a person worth waiting for

00:38:47.400 --> 00:38:48.360
See you tomorrow

00:38:48.480 --> 00:38:49.320
See you tomorrow

