Weren't you going to see the doctor?

00:38:55.800 --> 00:38:56.719
I'm not going

00:39:00.639 --> 00:39:01.960
Why won't you give up?

00:39:55.079 --> 00:39:56.320
If you're still alive

00:39:57.239 --> 00:39:58.559
If you can wake up

00:39:59.559 --> 00:40:01.039
If you've forgotten everything

00:40:01.840 --> 00:40:04.239
then you must remember these few things

00:40:05.559 --> 00:40:06.760
Never underestimate a man

00:40:06.760 --> 00:40:08.320
who reeks of duck grease

00:40:09.519 --> 00:40:11.000
Because within that smell of duck grease

00:40:11.000 --> 00:40:11.719
lies

00:40:12.519 --> 00:40:13.760
not just the responsibilities of a father

00:40:13.760 --> 00:40:14.400
a husband

00:40:14.400 --> 00:40:15.920
and a Big Brother

00:40:16.480 --> 00:40:17.800
but also the dream and tenacity

00:40:17.800 --> 00:40:19.159
to make a roast duck soar to the sky

00:40:21.480 --> 00:40:24.079
Never mock a single father with a daughter

00:40:25.159 --> 00:40:27.239
because he'll do something even crazier

00:40:27.800 --> 00:40:28.960
until you shut up

00:40:30.800 --> 00:40:33.239
Never let a fence-sitting yes-man

00:40:33.480 --> 00:40:34.920
grow into a great tree

00:40:35.719 --> 00:40:37.079
because when the storm comes

00:40:37.760 --> 00:40:39.239
he's tougher than any tree

