Remember

00:40:41.960 --> 00:40:43.199
the wooden frame's dimensions are

00:40:43.199 --> 00:40:44.599
thirty-six by forty-six

00:40:45.239 --> 00:40:46.480
Don't ask why

00:40:47.199 --> 00:40:49.239
because a female artist once said

00:40:49.400 --> 00:40:51.039
"Negative space is eternal"

