If you see an old screenwriter with a worried face

00:41:07.559 --> 00:41:08.719
remember to tell him

00:41:09.639 --> 00:41:11.840
there's a mission we shouldn't forget

00:41:12.599 --> 00:41:14.000
To be born human

00:41:14.280 --> 00:41:16.960
is not to endure suffering and misfortune

